name: vst.plantStatus
description: Any live, undamaged individual  (new, re-measured or ingrowth)

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Standing dead tree or standing dead bole within a multi-bole tree, regardless of cause of death. The entire tree or bole must be dead, and the main bole is NOT broken

name: vst.plantStatus
description: An individual that has been cut and removed by direct human activity related to harvesting, silviculture or land clearing (re-measurement plots only)

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Visible damage caused by insects; note 'crown' or 'bole' damage in remarks, and indicate type of insect causing damage if possible (e.g., mountain pine beetle, gypsy moth, etc.)

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Visible damage cause by disease; note 'crown' or 'bole' damage in remarks, and indicate type of disease causing damage if possible (e.g., Blister Rust, rot, canker, other (specify), unknown

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Visible damage not caused by disease or insects; note 'crown' or 'bole' damage in remarks, and indicate type of physical damage if possible (e.g., broken stem, bole scar, girdling, snow/ice damage, crushed, lightning, crown scorch, bole scorch)

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Visible damage of unknown origin; note 'crown' or 'bole' damage in remarks, and note cause if possible

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Individual is still alive and may qualify in the future, but does not currently qualify. Reason noted in remarks (e.g., consumption of qualifying boles / stems by fire, blow-down of qualifying boles / stems, etc.)

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Tree with broken spike top, tree with broken main bole and ascending leaders, tree broken and dead at top but live below

name: vst.plantStatus
description: All parts of the broken tree are dead; may have broken spike top, or dead leaders ascending beyond the break point. Indicate factors associated with death and the source of damage in order of importance in the remarks field

name: vst.plantStatus
description: A previously measured individual that is not measured in the current bout because the plot has been burned and the individual could not be located for remeasurement

name: vst.plantStatus
description: A previously measured individual that is not measured in the current bout because the individual could not be located for remeasurement. Cause of loss is presumed to be herbivory

name: vst.plantStatus
description: A previously measured individual that is not measured in the current bout because the individual could not be located for remeasurement, the individual is presumed dead based on evidence within the plot. Note in remarks reason (i.e. blowdown event)

name: vst.plantStatus
description: A previously measured individual that is not measured in the current bout due to inability to re-locate because of widespread damage to tags within a plot

name: vst.plantStatus
description: A previously measured individual that is not measured in the current bout note because the individual could not be relocated

name: vst.plantStatus
description: Part or all of a dead tree is down, and in contact with the ground. Percent of the bole in direct contact with the ground recorded in remarks
